==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hammer break
<hw>Ham"mer break</hw>. <fld>(Elec.)</fld> <def>An interrupter in which
contact is broken by the movement of an automatically vibrating hammer
between a contact piece and an electromagnet, or of a rapidly moving
piece mechanically driven.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hammercloth</ent>⟦br⟧
